WEBVTT

00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:02.816
(Applause)

00:03:02.840 --> 00:03:05.176
You like double oxymorons, huh?

00:03:05.200 --> 00:03:09.056
(Laughter)

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:15.176
(Applause)

00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:20.456
So this network, if given the request
to make a speech about AI,

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:23.120
he, or it, might say --

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:26.376
(Recording) Donald Trump:
It's a great thing

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:29.336
to build a better world
with artificial intelligence.

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:31.376
Kai-Fu Lee: And maybe in another language?